dct_description_sm: Lucas Aurigarius Inventor ; Ioannes à Doetecum fecít.
Relief shown pictorially; depths shown in bathymetric soundings.
Shows topography, vegetation, coastline, drainage, shoals, depths, anchorages, settlements (including ports).
Illustrations of flora, fauna, ship, sea monster.
